NODEACTION:COPY:<container>:NOCHILDREN	Copies just the specified node without copying its child nodes.
NODEACTION:COPY:<container>:UNIQUEONLY	If the node name is not unique in the destination container the node will not be copied. This option can be used with or without the NEWNAME option.
