POACTION:TRANSFER:REMOVE:<TransferID>	Removes the nodeID supplied in the data tag from a Transfer.

Expects a single NodeID or a List of NodeIDs as the data tag, and will remove the node(s) from the Transfer specified in the TransferID parameter.

