eg: [LL_REPTAG=DATAID POACTION:UPDATE:TO:[LL_REPTAG_DATE DATEINC:5:DAYS /] /]
REFRATE:<ReferenceRateCode>	Updates the Reference Rate property.
OFFSITEID:<newValue>	Updates the Offsite Storage ID property.
CLIENT:<newUser>	Updates the Client property. The new value can be passed a valid user login name or user ID.
eg: [LL_REPTAG=DATAID POACTION:UPDATE:CLIENT:1000 /]
or
[LL_REPTAG=DATAID POACTION:UPDATE:CLIENT:Admin /]
TEMPID:<newValue>	Updates the Temporary ID property.


Example:
The following will update the Locator Type property of the node that has a DataID of 12345:
[LL_REPTAG_"12345" POACTION:UPDATE:LOCTYPE:"LOCATORTYPE1" /]
