SETWFATTACH:MOVE:INHERITATTRS:DESTINATION	When the node is moved workflow categories and attributes are inherited from the workflow attachment folder
SETWFATTACH:MOVE:INHERITATTRS:MERGED	When the node is moved workflow categories and attributes are retained from the source node and merged with the categories and attributes of the workflow attachment folder
SETWFATTACH:MOVE:INHERITATTRS:SOURCE	When the node is moved workflow categories and attributes are retained from the source node.
