[LL_REPTAG_'X' SUBTRACT:Y /]
Type of X	Type of Y	Returns	Example
Integer or Real	Integer or Real	X - Y	[LL_REPTAG_'5' SUBTRACT:2.2 /]

returns 2.8
Date	Integer (seconds)	X - Y (date)	[LL_REPTAG_'May 2 2011' SUBTRACT:86400 /]

returns Sun May 01 00:00:00 2011
