WKSPINFO:RELATION:<relation type>:<single workspace type ID or list of workspace type IDs>	Returns the related business workspaces filtered by the relation type and their workspace type ID for the current workspace.

For example, WKSPINFO:RELATION:CHILD:{11,12} returns the related child business workspaces, which have the workspace type ID 11 or 12 for the current workspace.

Valid values for the <relation type> parameter are CHILD or PARENT.
See also: WKSPACTION   

		
